---
/**
 * Pricing page — /pricing
 * Grounded, transparent pricing with real cost comparison.
 * Tiers are illustrative; final prices TBD. See preview disclaimer below.
 *
 * Sources / date anchors (as of June 2026):
 *  - Shopify Basic: $39/mo (monthly) or $29/mo (annual) + 2.0% external-gateway fee
 *    Source: shopify.com/pricing + websitebuilderexpert.com
 *  - Medusa Cloud: Develop $29, Launch $99, Scale $299, Enterprise custom
 *    Source: docs.medusajs.com/cloud/pricing
 *  - Paystack SA: 2.9% + R1/transaction (local cards)
